setData.questStepSummary:
A Fishing Pond lies somewhere near a body of water in the Miasma in Savathn's throne world. Look at your map for the exact location where you can cast your line.

Fishing Ponds only appear while public events are not active in the same location.

Eris Morn is using the power tithed by the Guardians to find a way to defeat Xivu Arath and fulfill Savathn's bargain.

Deepen your understanding of the Hive by searching for cards from the Deck of Whispers ({var:3586210448} remaining).
